hands_on_practices.solution:
我们计算崩塌前的芯部加热。当 $r_c=\xi a$ 且 $P_\alpha=\kappa n_\alpha$ 时，
$$
W_{\rm before}
=\int_0^{r_c}P_\alpha(r)\,2\pi r\,dr
=\kappa2\pi n_0\int_0^{r_c}\Bigl(1-\frac{r^2}{a^2}\Bigr)r\,dr
=\kappa2\pi n_0\Bigl[\frac{r^2}{2}-\frac{r^4}{4a^2}\Bigr]_0^{r_c}
=\kappa2\pi n_0a^2\Bigl(\frac{\xi^2}{2}-\frac{\xi^4}{4}\Bigr).
$$

崩塌后，在 $r_{\rm mix}=\chi a$ 内部的密度被扁平化为平均值
$$
n_{\rm flat}
=\frac{\int_0^{r_{\rm mix}}n_0\,(1-r^2/a^2)\,2\pi r\,dr}{\pi r_{\rm mix}^2}
=n_0\Bigl(1-\frac{\chi^2}{2}\Bigr).
$$

因此
$$
W_{\rm after}
=\int_0^{r_c}\kappa n_{\rm flat}\,2\pi r\,dr
=\kappa2\pi n_0\Bigl(1-\frac{\chi^2}{2}\Bigr)\frac{r_c^2}{2}
=\kappa2\pi n_0a^2\frac{\xi^2}{2}\Bigl(1-\frac{\chi^2}{2}\Bigr).
$$

相对变化量为
$$
\Delta_f
=\frac{W_{\rm after}-W_{\rm before}}{W_{\rm before}}
=\frac{\kappa2\pi n_0a^2\Bigl[\frac{\xi^2}{2}(1-\frac{\chi^2}{2})
-\bigl(\frac{\xi^2}{2}-\frac{\xi^4}{4}\bigr)\Bigr]}
{\kappa2\pi n_0a^2\bigl(\frac{\xi^2}{2}-\frac{\xi^4}{4}\bigr)}
=\frac{\frac{\xi^4}{4}-\frac{\xi^2\chi^2}{4}}{\frac{2\xi^2-\xi^4}{4}}
=\frac{\xi^2-\chi^2}{2-\xi^2}.
$$
